<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Modern Landing Page</title>
    <style>
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box; /* Crucial for preventing overlapping and weird box sizes */
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }

        ul {
            list-style: none;
        }


        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px 8%;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #4f46e5; /* Main accent color */
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #4b5563;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: #4f46e5;
        }


        .cta-btn {
            background-color: #4f46e5;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }

        .cta-btn:hover {
            background-color: #4338ca;
        }

        .small-btn {
            padding: 8px 18px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .secondary-btn {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #4f46e5;
            border: 2px solid #4f46e5;
            padding: 11px 26px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .secondary-btn:hover {
            background-color: #4f46e5;
            color: #ffffff;
        }


        .hero {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            
            padding: 100px 8%; 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0e7ff 0%, #ffffff 100%);
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 800px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
        }

        .hero-buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .features-section {
            padding: 80px 8%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .features-section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .features-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 30px;
            flex-wrap: wrap; 
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            flex: 1; 
            min-width: 250px;
            padding: 35px 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
            border: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .feature-card .icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: #1f2937;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }


        footer {
            background-color: #111827;
            color: #9ca3af;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 8%;
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }


        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .navbar {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 15px;
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }
            
            .hero-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
            }
            
            .features-container {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header class="navbar">
        <div class="logo">LaunchPad</div>
        <nav>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">About</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
        <a href="#" class="cta-btn small-btn">Get Started</a>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>Build Your Future with Clean Code</h1>
                <p>Master HTML, CSS, and modern layouts to unleash your creativity. Create stunning, user-friendly designs that stand out from the crowd.</p>
                <div class="hero-buttons">
                    <a href="#" class="cta-btn">Start Learning</a>
                    <a href="#" class="secondary-btn">Learn More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="features" class="features-section">
            <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
            <div class="features-container">
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="icon">🚀</div>
                    <h3>Semantic Structure</h3>
                    <p>Clean, readable HTML5 tags that make your code accessible and optimized for search engines.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="icon">🎨</div>
                    <h3>Flexbox Layouts</h3>
                    <p>No overlapping nightmares. Align columns, align items, and manage spacing gracefully.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="icon">📱</div>
                    <h3>Responsive Design</h3>
                    <p>Crafted to look absolutely beautiful on desktops, tablets, and mobile screens alike.</p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 LaunchPad Tech. Built with passion and clean CSS.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
